What does this component render when used as `<Price amount={100} currency="EUR" />`?

```jsx
function Price({ amount, currency = "USD", showCents = true }) {
  const formatted = showCents ? amount.toFixed(2) : Math.round(amount);
  return <span>{formatted} {currency}</span>;
}
```

