What does this component display when used as `<Avatar name="Kim" size={48} />`?

```jsx
function Avatar({ name, size = 32, shape = "circle" }) {
  return (
    <img
      src={`/avatars/${name.toLowerCase()}.jpg`}
      alt={name}
      width={size}
      height={size}
      className={`avatar avatar-${shape}`}
    />
  );
}
```

Which props are required (have no default value) in this component?

```jsx
function Alert({ severity = "info", title, message, onClose, autoHide = false }) {
  return (
    <div className={`alert alert-${severity}`}>
      <strong>{title}</strong>
      <p>{message}</p>
      {onClose && <button onClick={onClose}>Close</button>}
    </div>
  );
}
```

